  "Description": {
    "English": "A slight membrane has begun to form over this viscous purple liquid. Beneath its glassy surface it swirls slowly, forming syrupy currents of its own accord.<br><br>The elixir will maintain your local <span class=\"name name-stellar\">boundary integrity</span> and prevent the intrusion of <span class=\"name name-special\">the horrors beyond</span>.<br><br>Consume the elixir with <span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span> or inject it directly into the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Anomaly Suppressor</span> from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "粘稠的紫色液体上逐渐形成了一层薄薄的膜。在玻璃般的外壳之下，里面的东西正在慢慢旋转并形成了一种糖浆的涡流。<br><br>灵药将能够维持本地的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">边界完整性</span>并避免<span class=\"name name-special\">边界之外的惧物</span>入侵。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>服下灵药，或者通过快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）将其注入<span class=\"name name-technology\">异象抑制器</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這種黏稠的紫色液體上已經形成了一層薄膜。玻璃般的外表下，裡面的濃稠液體緩緩旋轉，自動在薄膜中流動。<br><br>靈藥能維持局部<span class=\"name name-stellar\">邊界完整度</span>，並防止<span class=\"name name-special\">邊界外的懼獸</span>入侵。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span> 服用靈藥，或從快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 將其直接注入<span class=\"name name-technology\">異常抑制器</span>。"
  },
